data.title: St. Louis Blues
data.meta_description: St. Louis Blues | 34,209 followers on LinkedIn. The St. Louis Blues are a professional hockey team and member of the National Hockey League (NHL). Established in 1967, the Blues play in the NHL's Western Conference at Enterprise Center.
